title: SCP-6689-9
content:
[[include :scp-wiki:theme:basalt hidetitle=a]]

[[=image http://scpdsandbox.wdfiles.com/local--files/collab%3Adodo-maze/Path2.png width="550px"]]
[[div class="jotting"]]

The __[[[https://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/scp-6689/offset/2|path]]]__ set before you is yours to walk.

It must lead somewhere: from here to there.

Lay your trust in those that have preordained your traversal.

After all, continuing is __[[[https://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/scp-6689/offset/7|your choice]]]__ alone to make.
[[/div]]
author: DodoDevil
